Name: Average resolution time for 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time spent in 'Completed + Cancelled' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Earliest occurrence of 'Completed + Cancelled' after 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Latest occurrence of 'Completed + Cancelled' before 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to the start of any subsequent activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' in the context of the VINST system
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' in a single case
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Completed + Cancelled' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' leading to case re-opening
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Completed + Cancelled' in cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and the end of case where activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment occurs

Name: Time until first occurrence of 'Completed + Cancelled' from case initiation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average elapsed time between 'Completed + Cancelled' and any 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Total accumulated time of 'Completed + Cancelled' activities in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Median resolution time for 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Time variance for 'Completed + Cancelled' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Distribution of time intervals from 'Completed + Cancelled' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Comparison of average duration between 'Completed + Cancelled' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + Cancelled' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Standard deviation of time for 'Completed + Cancelled' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case
